submission_method: Mail or online through USCIS designated submission portals.
processing_time: Varies; typically several months depending on the type of petition and current workload.
fees: $460 application fee; additional fees may apply based on the visa type and processing method.
required_field_1_description: Name of the individual or organization submitting the petition.
required_field_2_description: Complete mailing address for the petitioner.
required_field_3_description: Unique number assigned by the IRS to the employer.
required_field_4_description: The classification symbol being requested for the beneficiary.
required_field_5_description: The action being requested, such as extension of stay or change of employer.
supporting_documents: Proof of the beneficiary's qualifications (e.g., degrees, certifications); Job offer letter from the petitioning employer; Evidence of the employer's ability to pay the offered wage; Form G-28, if applicable (Notice of Entry of Appearance as Attorney); Copy of the beneficiary's passport
